  "texts": [
    "The results showed that ChatGPT-4.0 outperformed in terms of accuracy, with 80.6% of the responses deemed 'good', surpassing 54.8% for Google).",
    "All the models showed high average comprehensiveness scores and significant self-correction capabilities (66.7% for ChatGPT-4.0% and 60% for Google Bard).",
    "This highlighted the potential of ChatGPT-4.0 and Google Bard to deliver essential answers to myopiarelated queries, although it is clear that their accuracy requires further enhancement and rigorous evaluation.",
    "In a recent investigation, the capacity of ChatGPT and Google Bard to generate professional-quality responses to inquiries regarding ocular symptoms were systematically examined (Pushpanathan et al., 2023).",
    "The answers procured were meticulously appraised and graded by ophthalmologists at the consultant level, based on criteria of accuracy, comprehensiveness, and self-awareness."
